<paragraph blockId="32.[264,1324,393,1379]" pageId="32" pageNumber="33">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[312,684,1113,1139]" pageId="32" pageNumber="33">Derivation of specific epithet.</emphasis>
From Greek 
<emphasis box="[846,918,1113,1138]" italics="true" pageId="32" pageNumber="33">oligos</emphasis>
for few, referring to the few long apical setae of the ovipositor.
</paragraph>
